{
  "uuid": "773d54038318f3f9b1c44c1fed769a46",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operations Manager for Club",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 8.30pm – 4.30am (Thur–Sat, Eve PH) / 8.30pm – 3.30am (other days)<br /><strong>Industry:</strong> Nightlife / F&B / Entertainment</p><h3>Role Summary</h3><p>We are opening a Tamil music dance club concept operating till 3–4am. We are looking for a highly disciplined and experienced Operations Manager to run full night operations, ensure licensing compliance, manage staff performance, control incidents, and drive nightly revenue through strong floor leadership.</p><p>This is not a desk role. You will be the person in charge on the ground during peak late-night operations.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Oversee full nightly operations from opening to closing (4am)</p></li><li><p>Ensure strict compliance with Public Entertainment Licence and Liquor Licence conditions</p></li><li><p>Lead and supervise bartenders, hosts, security, cashier and cleaner</p></li><li><p>Control crowd flow, customer behaviour and handle incidents decisively</p></li><li><p>Monitor table sales, bottle movement and overall revenue performance</p></li><li><p>Conduct pre-shift briefings and post-shift reporting</p></li><li><p>Manage cash handling and POS reconciliation with cashier</p></li><li><p>Work closely with security to prevent and de-escalate issues before they escalate</p></li><li><p>Ensure toilets, bar and floor cleanliness standards are maintained throughout the night</p></li><li><p>Maintain incident log and ensure proper documentation</p></li><li><p>Train and discipline staff to maintain service and safety standards</p></li><li><p>Liaise with DJ and floor supervisor to maintain proper energy flow in the venue</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 3 years experience in bar, club or late-night F&B operations</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership presence and ability to control difficult situations calmly</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Singapore licensing and nightlife regulations</p></li><li><p>Experience managing security and handling intoxicated customers</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working late hours till 4.30am</p></li><li><p>Strong cash control and operational discipline</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills and team management ability</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and alert for long night shifts</p></li></ul><h3>What We Are Looking For</h3><ul><li><p>Someone who can <strong>run the entire venue without the owner present</strong></p></li><li><p>Someone firm, street-smart, and respected by staff</p></li><li><p>Someone who understands that after 2am, safety and control are everything</p></li></ul>",
